Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs17\bord0\be2\shad0\c000000\b0\pos(225,132)}料理研已经\N\N\N\N\h失去了汤勺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs17\bord0\be2\shad0\c000000\b0\pos(225,156)}料理研已经\N\N\N\N\h失去了汤勺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs17\bord0\be2\shad0\c000000\b0\pos(225,162)}料理研已经\N\N\N\N\h失去了汤勺
